3 steps:-


####  1. Create the site on local machine #####

1. Start with open source bootstrap theme of ur choice 
2. Modify the index.html content as per your choice
3. Create a form from WUFOO.com which is nothing but a form buiilder and who takes care of databases and provides email notifications too.
4. In the portfolio you can also create a twitter follow button by calling out twitter follow button generator and embedding the code in your html doc as its is.


#### 2. Create Google analytics account to keep track of your website hits #####

#### 3. Deploy ur site on github by GithubWebsite Launch #####

### 4. Atom editor nad Sumome addon for sharing ur website ###